children.subject: do we get units for taking it as a student in the education branch?

history.content:
We’re Cloud at California, and we’re bringing cloud education and industry cloud experience to UC Berkeley. Whether you have no experience with cloud or programming, or you’re a seasoned developer, Cloud at California is for you!

Have no idea what the cloud is, but sounds interesting? We have an education branch that teaches you all you need to know about cloud technologies, allows you to progress as a cloud developer, and receive multiple AWS certifications. Already have experience with cloud? Join our consulting and development branch where you’ll get even more hands-on cloud development experience working on high-impact projects with growing startups.

Applications are due January 30th, Sunday at midnight, and can be found here!

Infosession 1: Monday, January 24th, 8:30-10 PM PST

Infosession 2: Wednesday, January 26th, 8:30-10 PM PST

Decisions will come out by February 4th!

Visit our website or our Facebook page for more information and updates.
